{"analytics_identifier":"OT1285","base_path":"/government/organisations/windrush-commemoration-committee","content_id":"5ee63249-c7a9-406a-b3e0-bcdc7e21437d","description":"We’re a group commissioned by the Prime Minister to provide advice on how best to create a permanent and fitting tribute to the Windrush generation and their descendants. Windrush Commemoration Committee is part of the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We’re a group commissioned by the Prime Minister to provide advice on how best to create a permanent and fitting tribute to the Windrush generation and their descendants.</p>\n\n<p>Windrush Commemoration Committee is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government\">Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Windrush Commemoration Committee"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/windrush-commemoration-committee/about/membership","title":"Membership"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/national-windrush-monument-unveiled-at-london-waterloo-station","image":{"alt_text":"Basil Watson and sculpture","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62bb08fed3bf7f6623b93a6e/s712_s960_Basil_working_on_sculpture_960.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62bb08fe8fa8f57210d03be6/s465_s960_Basil_working_on_sculpture_960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62bb08fee90e0721c489682a/s960_Basil_working_on_sculpture_960.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2022-06-22T11:01:16.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Members of the Windrush generation joined HRH Duke and Duchess of Cambridge at London Waterloo Station today to witness the unveiling of the National Windrush Monument.</p>\n</div>","title":"National Windrush monument unveiled at London Waterloo Station"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/35-projects-across-england-awarded-funding-from-windrush-day-grant-scheme-2022","image":{"alt_text":"Windrush 2022 logo","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62aca9cde90e0765da021334/s712_s960_Windrush_2022.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62aca9cde90e0765d091f22f/s465_s960_Windrush_2022.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62aca9cdd3bf7f0af5de3929/s960_Windrush_2022.png"},"public_updated_at":"2022-05-20T09:30:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Events helping remember and recognise the leading role the Windrush Generation and their descendants have played in making Britain stronger, culturally richer and more inclusive.</p>\n</div>","title":"35 projects across England awarded funding from Windrush Day Grant Scheme 2022"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/basil-watson-chosen-to-design-national-windrush-monument","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6169368d8fa8f52982a860eb/s712_Basil_Sculpture_960.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6169368de90e07197f18fcaa/s465_Basil_Sculpture_960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6169368d8fa8f5297d57de19/Basil_Sculpture_960.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2021-10-15T00:15:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Internationally renowned artist Basil Watson has been chosen to design the National Windrush Monument, which will stand at London Waterloo station.</p>\n</div>","title":"Basil Watson chosen to design national Windrush Monument"},{"document_type":"Detailed guide","href":"/guidance/windrush-